{"tid":1007686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"帶防狼噴霧係犯法","createTime":"2019-02-04T02:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T03:44:47.000Z","uid":5822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4139d1e44ce3bdf3415a3cf1233968dc37c0f51","tid":1007686,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/191962/台女攜防狼噴霧遊香港迪士尼被捕-律師-自衛用途也可能誤墮法網\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F191962%2F%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E6%94%9C%E9%98%B2%E7%8B%BC%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E9%81%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%A4%E5%A2%AE%E6%B3%95%E7%B6%B2&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToCF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=6343cdcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/191962/台女攜防狼噴霧遊香港迪士尼被捕-律師-自衛用途也可能誤墮法網</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主在警局錄口供及筆錄簽名，用電腦畫押十根手指頭及手掌，手持上面寫有名字跟案名的A4紙及拍全身照，在拘留室待了7個小時，直至繳交保釋金後才被放出，翌日要到法院認罪，並繳交罰金1000元港幣。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，只是攜帶了在台灣極為普遍的「防狼噴霧器」，但這物品在香港卻列爲違禁品，認爲香港應該多在網站上宣導。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">她又曾問及警察「女生怎麼自保」，對方回應指「我們香港很安全的沒有人會想動歪腦筋」。</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c7f0e40ebdf2ee493e10aa59c23c3c07e0cdab5","tid":1007686,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"【警隊年結】被捕警務人員增55%　一哥：成因包括不恰當性慾望<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/289029/%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%90-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%A2%9E55-%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5-%E6%88%90%E5%9B%A0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%B0%E7%95%B6%E6%80%A7%E6%85%BE%E6%9C%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F289029%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E8%25A